item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Oracle TimesTen In-Memory Database Support User's Guide
item.description: Describes how to use Oracle SQL Developer with Oracle TimesTen In-Memory Database. This document is released with SQL Developer, not with TimesTen. Release number above refers to SQL Developer release number.

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Oracle TimesTen In-Memory Database Support Release Notes
item.description: Provides late-breaking information about Oracle SQL Developer for Oracle TimesTen In-Memory Database. This document is released with SQL Developer, not with TimesTen. Release number above refers to SQL Developer release number.

item.title: Oracle® Data Miner Installation and Administration Guide
item.description: Provides information for installing and administering the Data Miner repository and for using the repository APIs.

item.title: Oracle® Data Miner Release Notes
item.description: Describes new features, enhancements, bug fixes, prerequisites, and limitations in the current release of Oracle Data Miner.

item.title: Oracle® Data Miner User's Guide
item.description: Provides conceptual and usage information about Oracle Data Miner, a workflow-based graphical interface to Oracle Data Mining.

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer User's Guide
item.description: Provides conceptual and usage information about Oracle SQL Developer, a graphical tool that enables you to browse, create, edit, and delete (drop) database objects; run SQL statements and scripts; edit and debug PL/SQL code; manipulate and export data; migrate third-party databases to Oracle; view metadata and data in MySQL and third-party databases; and view and create reports.

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Data Modeler User's Guide
item.description: Provides conceptual and usage information about Oracle SQL Developer Data Modeler, a data modeling and database design tool that provides an environment for capturing, modeling, managing, and exploiting metadata.

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Installation Guide
item.description: Provides information for installing the Oracle SQL Developer tool on Windows, Linux, and Mac OS X systems.

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Command-Line Quick Reference
item.description: Describes features of SQL Developer Command-Line (SQLcl).

item.title: Oracle® SQL Developer Data Modeler Accessibility Guide
item.description: Accessibility features for Oracle SQL Developer Data Modeler.

item.description: Accessibility Features for Oracle SQL Developer.
